list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Add distributed training scripts and update related codes
This update introduces distributed training scripts to facilitate better handling of large scale data sets. Code has also been modified to better align with PyTorch's distributed data parallelism (DDP) guidelines. Additionally, it adds a new loader for training and testing, integrates a kernel-based learning algorithm, and implements support for NVIDIA's Automatic Mixed Precision (AMP) in the training process.
